author: Jonathan Sawyer
title: Hiroshi Fujiwara Teases New fragment design x Louis Vuitton Collaboration
text:
Share Tweet Email WhatsApp Comments 
Hiroshi Fujiwara continues to tease items from fragment design’s forthcoming Louis Vuitton collaboration , today taking to social media to preview what appears to be a new varsity jacket. 
The black and white outerwear boasts white co-branding on the chest, in addition to multicolored tagging on the sleeve. A photo posted by fujiwarahiroshi (@fujiwarahiroshi) on Jan 19, 2017 at 1:09pm PST 
The Instagram post arrives with no caption, meaning no information surrounding the upcoming fragment design x Louis Vuitton goods. Per usual, you’ll have to check back with us for more.
